@startuml
title E Visa Processing And Follow Up System — Polished Requirement Specification


[*] --> J1

state "Create an account" as CreateAccount
CreateAccount : entry / User wants to create an account
CreateAccount : do / Verify details
CreateAccount : exit / Account created

state "Login" as Login
Login : entry / Registered user
Login : do / Verify password
Login : exit / View details

state "Apply for a visa" as ApplyVisa
ApplyVisa : entry / User wants to apply for a visa
ApplyVisa : do / Make payment and accept application
ApplyVisa : exit / Application accepted

state "View status" as ViewStatus
ViewStatus : entry / User wants to view the status of their application
ViewStatus : do / Display status
ViewStatus : exit / Status viewed

state "Check status" as CheckStatus
CheckStatus : entry / User wants to check the status of their application
CheckStatus : do / Verify status
CheckStatus : exit / Status checked

state "Cancel an application" as CancelApplication
CancelApplication : entry / User wants to cancel their application
CancelApplication : do / Cancel application
CancelApplication : exit / Application cancelled

state "Modify details" as ModifyDetails
ModifyDetails : entry / User wants to modify their details
ModifyDetails : do / Update details
ModifyDetails : exit / Details modified

state "View details" as ViewDetails
ViewDetails : entry / User wants to view their details
ViewDetails : do / Display details
ViewDetails : exit / Details viewed

state "View purpose of application" as ViewPurpose
ViewPurpose : entry / User wants to view the purpose of their application
ViewPurpose : do / Verify document check
ViewPurpose : exit / Status updated

state "Give feedback" as GiveFeedback
GiveFeedback : entry / User wants to give feedback on their application status
GiveFeedback : do / Add feedback
GiveFeedback : exit / Feedback given

state "Log out" as Logout
Logout : entry / User wants to log out of the system
Logout : do / End session
Logout : exit / Log out successful


J1 --> CreateAccount
CreateAccount --> J2

state "Register" as Register
Register : entry / New user
Register : do / Verify details
Register : exit / Verified details

J2 --> [*] : [Invalid Credentials]
J2 --> Login : [Valid]

Login --> [*] : [Improper]
Login --> ViewDetails : [Proper]

ViewDetails --> J3

state "Add case" as AddCase
AddCase : entry / Wants to add case
AddCase : do / Show Category
AddCase : exit / Selects a category

J3 --> ApplyVisa
ApplyVisa --> CheckStatus
CheckStatus --> GiveFeedback

state "Civil" as Civil
Civil : entry / Selects this category
Civil : do / update view table
Civil : exit / Allows to add details

state "Criminal" as Criminal
Criminal : entry / Selects this category
Criminal : do / Update the view table
Criminal : exit / Allows to add details

ApplyVisa --> ViewStatus
ViewStatus --> CheckStatus
CheckStatus --> GiveFeedback
GiveFeedback --> Logout


Logout --> [*]

@enduml
